data.summary_suggestion: Send content to display on terminal screen
data.description_suggestion: Sends content to be displayed on one or more display devices of a payment terminal. The request specifies the DisplayOutput elements containing text, images, or formatted content for each device type (CashierInterface, CustomerInterface, or other display devices). Returns confirmation of successful display rendering. Used for showing transaction information, prompts, or messages to cashier or customer.
